Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I... pass out?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move an inch.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:40.40,0:02:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already noon?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.74,0:02:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My whole body feels so cold.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:46.42,0:02:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I sick?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.35,0:02:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And this just had to happen when Haqua was gone.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.32,0:02:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it, I wasn't feeling well yesterday either.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:55.25,0:02:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And spending the night in the library must have made it worse.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.18,0:03:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn, maybe I shouldn't have come back home
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.21,0:03:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}after drawing out Shiori's goddess.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.74,0:03:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there's no point in regretting my decision now!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:07.38,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to get to school.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.96,0:03:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Within either Chihiro or Ayumi resides the final goddess, Mercurius.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.73,0:03:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I found him, Nora{-san}.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.50,0:03:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's sleeping.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.36,0:03:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.65,0:03:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy is likely the key to all this.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.78,0:03:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on him, Ryou.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.06,0:03:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger. Just leave it all to your brilliant buddy over here.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.38,0:03:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nora's stupid buddy.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.38,0:03:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Ryou, you know. Asama Ryou.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing he—
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.84,0:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you grab that cell phone for me?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I only take orders from Nora{-san}.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Cell. Phone. Now.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.64,0:03:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.45,0:03:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what're you doing? What're you doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting the event.
