Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.24,0:04:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ellie.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.53,0:04:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not coming to school today?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.73,0:04:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What about band practice?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:11.76,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Ayumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.31,0:04:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.99,0:04:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.91,0:04:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you using Ellie's phone?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.55,0:04:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Elsie asked me to call you.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.27,0:04:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Something came up, so she won't be at school today.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Something came up?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.03,0:04:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone but me is away,\N attending a memorial service.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Elsie won't be...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.89,0:04:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't sound too good.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.29,0:04:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My head kinda hurts... Did you say something?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.20,0:04:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Never mind!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.02,0:04:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.35,0:05:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's enough to get her to visit.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.17,0:05:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a call?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.64,0:05:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm starving!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.48,0:05:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to get a drink. I'm gonna go buy one.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please visit me, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.34,0:05:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
