Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.33,0:05:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a "sick visit" event?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.39,0:05:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The sick visit is as classic an event as there is.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.77,0:05:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can track your progress \Nby seeing if a girl visits or not.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.64,0:05:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the perfect chance to advance,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.83,0:05:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because I really {\i1}am{\i0} sick!
