Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.73,0:05:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Chihiro?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.89,0:05:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Ellie?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you at school today?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.82,0:05:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was thinking of dropping off that music I mentioned, if that's okay...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.04,0:05:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sounds like Chihiro hasn't found out yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.67,0:05:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But how come you're not at school? Are you sick?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.52,0:05:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't have them both visit at the same time.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.92,0:05:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Want me to bring you some sweets?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.25,0:05:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Elsie isn't home right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi? What are {\i1}you{\i0} doing there?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of the family went \Nto a memorial service today.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.83,0:06:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No point visiting someone who isn't here, stupid.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That should keep her away for now.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll try getting her to stop by later tonight, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.53,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't have to call me stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.68,other hand,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.2\fs5\blur1.2\b1\frz2.163\c&H9898B7&\fscx3709\fscy5823.13\pos(611,597)}Light Music Club
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.10,0:06:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna stop somewhere on the way home?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.09,0:06:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui, how about grabbing some taiyaki?{great now i can't see 'taiyaki' and keep a straight face}{lmao. hot pocket obv}{poptart #1}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.79,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I gotta go straight home.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you, Ayumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.14,0:06:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go straight home too.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are no fun!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.58,0:06:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do {\i1}I{\i0} have to stand watch outside?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I should just go home.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.89,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.28,0:07:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, of course not.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.20,0:07:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... Is anyone home?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.33,0:07:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I didn't think getting water would be so hard.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.49,Alternative,,0,0,0,,K-Katsuragi!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.78,0:07:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ayumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.26,0:07:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't worried about you or anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.46,0:07:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were coughing so hard,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to make sure you weren't dying.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.04,0:07:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said before, I don't wanna talk to you anymore!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My room.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.95,0:07:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really home alone?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.12,0:07:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, my family won't be back for a while.{isn't this a comma splice?}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.96,0:07:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fine then.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.25,0:07:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're {\i1}that{\i0} sick, I can't just ditch you.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Up we go.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.42,0:07:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're burning up.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.10,0:08:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect your room to be so messy.
