Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.04,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.51,round5,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\bord1.5\an4\blur0.5\3c&HE6E6E6&\c&HE6E6E6&\pos(456,558)\b1\1a&HFF&\t(455,500,\1a&H00&)}Arrangement by: Ryou
