Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.36,0:08:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You should keep your room a bit tidier.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:19.86,0:08:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be embarrassing for visitors to see this mess, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.86,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No one ever visits me.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying. People visit you.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.69,0:08:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I was a little happy that you came to check on me.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a little? That's kinda mean.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.54,0:08:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She left?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.24,0:08:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that you wanted water, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.22,0:08:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you some.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Is this okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.08,0:08:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you sit up on your own?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.17,0:09:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.42,0:09:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Don't spill it.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's a cute cup.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:09.53,0:09:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense, since there's a café downstairs—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.50,0:09:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you hold it tightly.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.74,0:09:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.24,0:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't expect it to go this well.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this the power of the sick visit event?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then{,} I'll take this as far as I can!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.19,0:09:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You have to stay in bed.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.69,0:09:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to get better soon, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.42,0:09:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, make sure you keep yourself warm.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.07,0:09:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:42.22,0:09:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you... stay a little longer?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.88,0:09:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess I can.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:50.23,0:09:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good! I feel like crap, but I can take it from here with my eyes closed.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.01,0:09:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time to max Ayumi's affection level!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.65,0:10:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The doorbell rang.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like answering it.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.18,0:10:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretend no one's home.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.93,0:10:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.75,0:10:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.72,0:10:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ch-Chihiro?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.62,0:10:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-Why is Chihiro here?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I took specific steps to ensure she wouldn't come!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.27,0:10:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she sees me with Ayumi...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm screwed!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Nora's stupid buddy! Do something!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No answer...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.67,0:10:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had something I wanted to drop off.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.20,0:10:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone home?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.52,0:10:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If a girl shows up, let me know!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.45,0:10:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need anything, you should tell the other buddy.{dammit ryou}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:40.14,0:10:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's waiting for you upstairs.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.29,0:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddy?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.12,0:10:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That moron! What is he {\i0}doing{\i1}?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.12,0:10:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If I've completed a mission once, \NI can repeat it without having to be told!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:48.61,0:10:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes me special.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.74,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Upstairs?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those Ellie's?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so messy.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.43,0:11:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have time to send Ayumi home.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That would only lower her affection level.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to do something.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.09,0:11:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make a sound!{uh...}{lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.20,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:34.26,0:11:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why are you here?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:37.27,0:11:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that Elsie isn't home, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.74,0:11:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chihiro?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.26,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ellie asked me for some sheet music.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:50.96,0:11:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you give her this?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.81,0:11:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.50,0:11:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look so good, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.07,0:11:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.08,0:12:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you go downstairs and get me some medicine?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.73,0:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You really {\i1}are{\i0} sick?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:04.80,0:12:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a cold.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.92,0:12:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rotten luck, getting sick when everyone's out of the house...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.59,0:12:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.29,0:12:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why did I have to hide?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.12,0:12:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm not comfortable with other people seeing us together.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.72,0:12:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be worse if she sees us on the bed together!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.13,0:12:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll have to hide until Chihiro leaves.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Our honor is at stake here.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:36.67,0:12:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our{\i0} honor? This is all {\i1}your{\i0} fault!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.50,0:12:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.63,0:12:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the medicine you wanted?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.79,0:12:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just over-the-counter stuff...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.58,0:12:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.25,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Katsuragi, this is really awkward... U-Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:54.86,0:12:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you keep your voice down? My head's killing me.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.33,0:13:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, shouldn't you see a doctor?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.64,0:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It all happened so fast that I didn't get the chance to.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.41,0:13:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a serious fever!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.32,0:13:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are they doing? I can't hear a thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to open it for you?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.57,0:13:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nicer than I expected.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.29,0:13:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Than you expected?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:26.08,0:13:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this what anyone would do for someone who's sick?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:29.65,0:13:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.43,0:13:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your concern...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.64,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Concern... Well, I just...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.60,0:13:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm impressed this is going so well.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.68,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Despite my poor condition and a critical accident,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:53.01,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still raising their affection levels.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.79,0:13:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can pull this off! The double sick visit event!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.30,0:14:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi, you seem awfully bulky.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.38,0:14:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was shivering, so I added an extra blanket.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.76,0:14:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A blanket?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shivering? Are you cold?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.44,0:14:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll turn on the heat.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.54,0:14:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When you have a cold, it's important to keep yourself warm.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.03,0:14:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.93,0:14:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.49,0:14:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to get dehydrated, so I'll get you some water.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.75,0:14:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.40,0:14:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, why do I have to do this?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:34.79,0:14:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too hot!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.43,0:14:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you pour water on yourself?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.20,0:14:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I sweat a lot!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.03,0:14:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.08,0:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You liar.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.14,0:14:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You said no one was coming to visit you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.24,0:14:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Chihiro's here to see Elsie.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.09,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.81,0:15:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You called me a blanket!{lol}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.55,0:15:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.54,0:15:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.98,0:15:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.20,0:15:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your legs are sticking out.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.47,0:15:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be wearing sweatpants or something?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:14.82,0:15:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my choice!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So hot...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.70,0:15:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How did she not notice that they weren't my legs?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.23,0:15:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe that'd just be too absurd?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.37,0:15:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.17,0:15:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,do you remember that song from the other day?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.69,0:15:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When was that?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.26,0:15:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In the music shop, remember?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.54,0:15:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.80,0:15:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've f-finished the next part,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.08,0:15:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so I wanted you to hear it...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.96,0:15:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're not feeling well, it can wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:49.10,0:15:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:49.83,0:15:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't she come to see Elsie?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She {\i1}did{\i0} come to see you!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Are you okay, Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:59.73,0:16:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My stomach's hurting a little...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.93,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let me hear your song.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.06,0:16:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You don't have to if you're feeling sick.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.52,0:16:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This cold is nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.50,0:16:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your song is more important.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:17.65,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't expect anything special.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.32,0:16:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wasn't part of my plan,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.43,0:16:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but the completion of that song is a crucial event.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.71,0:16:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to put Chihiro first, \Neven if I lose points with Ayumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.04,0:16:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The song is basically finished, \Nbut I don't have any lyrics yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:36.42,0:16:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All right, here I go.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.39,0:16:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.13,0:17:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I usually only listen to game soundtracks,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.48,0:17:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but I really like your song.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.94,0:17:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to play it at the Mai High Festival?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be done in time.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.63,0:17:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The festival's in three days.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm gonna head off.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.83,0:18:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:04.77,0:18:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.33,0:18:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you for listening to my song, even though you're sick.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.58,0:18:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks like I survived.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.62,0:18:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I made good progress with Chihiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.76,0:18:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, for...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.06,0:18:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayumi! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My shirt's see-through!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh! Don't look, you jerk!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.76,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You slimeball! I hope that cold kills you!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you always so angry?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.78,0:18:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one who made me angry!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.18,0:18:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't lying. I really didn't know she was coming.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.99,0:18:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's nothing going on between you and Chihiro?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.85,0:19:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that I...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.64,0:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to tell you something.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.82,0:19:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,in love with you.{oh snap}{always drops this when it's most convenient. oh, Keima.}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:24.33,0:19:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So... T-Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.54,0:19:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:32.46,0:19:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I nodded off for a moment, \Nso I didn't catch what you said.{I JUST REMEMBERED I HAD SOMETHING TO DO! SEE YOU!!!}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.32,0:19:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Chihiro?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.32,0:19:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Never mind!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.36,0:19:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.01,0:19:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you listening, Ayumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.14,0:20:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Chihiro say?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.44,0:20:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.49,0:20:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't hear it?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.91,0:20:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I should get going.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.25,0:20:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:14.42,0:20:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from you hitting me under the blankets...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.37,0:20:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? You're blaming {\i1}me{\i0}?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:20.42,0:20:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let Ayumi leave now.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.02,0:20:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't give her time to think.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.99,0:20:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, I can't believe Chihiro...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That confession caught me completely by surprise.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.80,0:20:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(0,850)}I can't handle this on my own!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.95,0:20:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only Haqua were here.{<3}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.48,0:20:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.68,0:20:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she still upstairs?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her I had to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.56,0:20:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)\i1}I misjudged Chihiro's affection level.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.96,0:20:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)\i1}And those two are close friends, which just complicates things.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.42,0:20:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this point, my only option is to choose one and go all-in.
