Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.65,0:21:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:09.15,0:21:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in love with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.73,0:21:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I actually heard you.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard your confession.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.18,0:21:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:24.62,0:21:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.67,0:21:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Chihiro, answer the phone!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:32.06,0:21:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chihiro, are you in love with Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:39.08,0:21:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, you heard?!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.59,0:21:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you hear?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:44.59,0:21:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard some rumors...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:47.00,0:21:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:48.48,0:21:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:50.73,0:21:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you right now, Ayumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:53.03,0:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, I'm... Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:57.05,0:21:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:59.02,0:22:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of confessed my feelings...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:04.35,0:22:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:06.05,0:22:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I just lost it for a moment.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:09.05,0:22:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was mostly talking to myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:11.44,0:22:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't listening anyway.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:14.13,0:22:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what came over me.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:16.53,0:22:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I've asked so many guys out that I'll go for anyone now!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:21.09,0:22:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't true.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:25.59,0:22:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You've found true love.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:30.08,0:22:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm rooting for you!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:40.51,0:22:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:42.08,0:22:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:46.29,0:22:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ayumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:51.96,0:22:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling better?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:53.91,0:22:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, much better.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:55.58,0:22:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:57.06,0:22:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm going home.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:01.36,0:23:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My cold's getting worse again...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:08.77,0:23:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:09.88,0:23:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask Chihiro to come and take care of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:13.46,0:23:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? It isn't working?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:16.64,0:23:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayumi, are you mad?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:19.05,0:23:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I be mad?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:21.77,0:23:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Be nice to Chihiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:24.02,0:23:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:30.10,0:23:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ayumi isn't angry anymore?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:32.48,0:23:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And she keeps bringing up Chihiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:35.45,0:23:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't get it,
Dialogue: 5,0:23:37.00,0:23:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I have a really bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:43.03,0:23:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:45.62,0:23:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...should I do now?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:49.10,0:23:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it is what it is.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:54.51,0:23:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Ayumi...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:56.26,0:24:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,at Katsuragi's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:19.85,eptitle,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\pos(640,695)\shad0.5\4c&H000000&\4a&HC0&\fscx90\fscy90}Goddess Mix
Dialogue: 5,0:24:06.67,0:24:07.67,Default,,0,0,130,,Chihiro and Ayumi.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:07.67,0:24:10.07,Default,,0,0,130,,They're classmates, bandmates, and best friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:10.07,0:24:12.71,Default,,0,0,130,,So I must exercise the utmost care when conquering them.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:12.71,0:24:13.64,Default,,0,0,130,,This is such a pain!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:13.64,0:24:16.64,Default,,0,0,130,,If the last goddess were in someone like Haqua, this would be much easier.{YES YES YES}{well, she's a goddess anyway}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:16.64,0:24:20.24,Default,,0,0,130,,Huh? Where did she go, anyway?
